{"tid":611482,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"台灣中正大學畢典廢除「唱國歌」及「向國旗暨國父遺像行三鞠躬禮」  全台灣僅剩台大及台北大學2大學還有","createTime":"2018-03-31T05:08:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-31T07:31:55.000Z","uid":35790,"like":16,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"72fc672a0c1e5dfc3be19bed4618c8d6a1bce8d3","tid":611482,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T05:08:34.000Z","msg":"中正大學畢典廢唱國歌 全台僅剩2大學還有<br />\n<br />\n2018-03-31 10:50聯合報 記者林良齊╱即時報導<br />\n<br />\n近年來不少人認為在畢業典禮唱國歌、對國父遺像行三鞠躬禮等是威權象徵，而去年中正大學的畢業典禮也有僑外生在畢典抗議，中正大學行政會議也在近日的行政會議上，確認畢業典禮流程時廢除「唱國歌」及「向國旗暨國父遺像行三鞠躬禮」，目前全台僅剩台灣大學及台北大學在畢典還有類似的流程。<br />\n<br />\n中正大學學生會近日在臉書上指出「以往畢業典禮流程中，均有「唱國歌」與「向國旗暨國父遺像行三鞠躬禮」等約5分鐘的儀式」，而在「今年3月26日第450次行政會議中，學務處針對上述儀式之存廢提請討論，主席校長裁示本年度畢業典禮取消下列儀式，唱國歌及向國旗暨國父遺像行三鞠躬禮」，希望藉由取消以往總被視為理所當然的儀式，學校可以讓畢業生參與一場更多元、友善的畢業典禮。"},{"pid":"83061a5e859c02e8acbf142931fdcc944a411e43","tid":611482,"uid":35790,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T05:11:39.000Z","msg":"香港將立有罰則國歌法<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6edd683ca842e9683efa07d8566ece3751bb9fb","tid":611482,"uid":33263,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T05:39:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好事<br />\n國民黨殺人犯"},{"pid":"e0ed648cf424d24ec01a5f5ff3fcb495e7869446","tid":611482,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T05:42:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpsAfd2M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpsAfd2M.jpg&h=c1dea681&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n國民政府明令規定以中國國民黨黨歌為中華民國國歌，通令知照，並轉飭所屬一體知照。（國史館提供）"},{"pid":"1dc67a3f948f0bbed85f0c438c5a75a3cda82fdc","tid":611482,"uid":17765,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"b6edd683ca842e9683efa07d8566ece3751bb9fb","tid":611482,"uid":33263,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T05:39:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好事<br />\n國民黨殺人犯"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T05:42:59.000Z","msg":"香港閪日笑夜笑嘅台仔識進步<br />\n香港閪自己就開倒車<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95d51e2106ca57fe59dbf4861857ad2e8917ddf2","tid":611482,"uid":33263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1dc67a3f948f0bbed85f0c438c5a75a3cda82fdc","tid":611482,"uid":17765,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"b6edd683ca842e9683efa07d8566ece3751bb9fb","tid":611482,"uid":33263,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T05:39:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好事<br />\n國民黨殺人犯"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T05:42:59.000Z","msg":"香港閪日笑夜笑嘅台仔識進步<br />\n香港閪自己就開倒車<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T05:53:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"227416be19ecccb2011dbe7402e8bad4e1159c50","tid":611482,"uid":35790,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"95d51e2106ca57fe59dbf4861857ad2e8917ddf2","tid":611482,"uid":33263,"l